                     ID BR_1
Summary: The search field placeholder text doesn’t update when changing the interface language Eng/ Ukr.
Environment: 
OS: Windows 11
Browser: Chrome v.141.0.7390.77 
            Preconditions:
Open oxford-med.com.ua website 
Steps to reproduce:
Switch interface language to Eng/Ukr
Click on the search sign
Check the placeholder text
Actual result:
            The search field placeholder text is displayed in the Russian language.
            Expected result:
            The search field placeholder text is displayed in the English/Ukrainian language.
            Attachments: 

Severity: Low
Priority: High

